    "n_guide_content_8qFAbx": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Product Claims & User Study",
        "text": "<h2>Product Claims & User Study</h2><p>Skin Rejuvenation Treatment:</p><ul><li>Helps support natural collagen for smoother, plumper-looking skin</li><li>Visibly refines texture and improves the look of firmness and elasticity</li><li>Enhances radiance and promotes a more even-toned appearance</li><li>Helps reduce the appearance of redness</li></ul><p>Skin Clearing Treatment:</p><ul><li>Blue and red light wavelengths shown in studies to help reduce mild-to-moderate acne</li><li>Helps balance oil and improve the look of clearer skin</li><li>Visibly soothes and calms post-breakout skin</li></ul><p>Findings from independent LED light studies:</p><ul><li>Up to 87% of participants reported <strong>smoother-looking skin</strong> and reduced fine lines</li><li>97% noticed <strong>visibly improved skin tone</strong> and enhanced smoothness</li><li>83% reported <strong>fewer visible breakouts</strong> after consistent use</li></ul><p>Insights supported by independent published studies on red, blue, and near-infrared light wavelengths commonly used in cosmetic LED therapy.</p>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_ntcFrF": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "blocks": {
        "quote_cpz4xi": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "style": "blue",
            "text": "<p>Remember to <strong>add a personal touch</strong> to the messaging, talk about how the mask fits into your routine or how your skin has changed.</p><p>Examples:</p><ul><li>“This mask changed my skin.”</li><li>“My breakouts have calmed down so much since using this.”</li><li>“My skin looks smoother and more even after just a few weeks.”</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
